<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nsbḥ ạsmk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- nsbḥ ạsmk yạ mn ṣlbt lạ̉jlnạ
 nsbḥ ạsmk ạ̉ḥzạnnạ ḥmlthạ
 nsbḥ ạsmk yạ mn ṣʿdt bnạ
 ạ̹ly̱ ạlsmạʾ mntṣryn
 1- nsbḥk ʿly̱ ạldwạm .. fqd sḥqt lnạ ạlsẖyṭạn
 wnhtf wạtẖqyn
 nsqṭ kl ạlạ̉swạr .. bạ̹ymạn wạ̹ṣrạr
 bạ̉smk sạḥqyn ạ̉ʿdạỷnạ
 2- nrfʿ ạ̉ṣwạtnạ .. nʿln nṣrtnạ
 wnsẖdw frḥyn
 hybtk ạ̉mạmnạ .. trʿb ạ̉ʿdạỷnạ
 wfyk mntṣryn hllwyạ
 3- nʿẓmk yạ rbnạ .. brwḥk gẖmrtnạ
 fnkẖdm mmswḥyn
 kl qwtk lnạ .. slṭạnk mnḥtnạ
 wfyk mmtlỷyn brwḥk</lyrics>
<author>hạlẗ ʿzyz wswzy̱ yʿqwb, lḥn ạ̉jnby</author>
<hymn_number>185</hymn_number>
</song>